---
import PhotoPlaceholder from './PhotoPlaceholder.astro';
---

<section class="bg-mid py-14 md:py-24">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="feature-grid reverse">
      <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden h-[280px] md:h-[420px]">
        <PhotoPlaceholder label="RoofBlue RETAIN System Photo" class="h-full" iconSize={40} />
      </div>
      <div class="feature-text">
        <span class="tag">Blue-Vegetative Roof Research</span>
        <h2>RoofBlue RETAIN&trade; — Stormwater, Solved</h2>
        <p>
          A 2022 study by world-renowned vegetative roof researcher Brad Rowe found that RoofBlue RETAIN
          — combined with LiveRoof Standard or Lite modules — increases stormwater retention by over
          25%.
        </p>
        <p>
          The same system enhances plant growth and reduces irrigation requirements, making it one of
          the most impactful upgrades available for any vegetative roof installation.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2.5 my-6">
          <span class="chip blue">25%+ More Retention</span>
          <span class="chip green">Reduced Irrigation</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3.5 flex-wrap">
          <a href="/products/roofblue" class="btn btn-primary">White Paper</a>
          <a href="/products/roofblue" class="btn-outline-dark btn">RoofBlue RETAIN</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
